1.Bug Reproduce.
	crashing between the snapshot taking and write epoch file causes restart fails.

2.Original Bug Report.
	https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZooKeeper-1653

3.Manual Patch.
	https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12575121/ZOOKEEPER-1653.patch

4.Input for DFix.
	./input directory
	./input/config : bug report.
	./input/jarpath : app jar files location.
	./input/srcpath	: app source code location.
	
5.DFix Patch.
	./patch directory. see the detail.patch file.

6.Discussion.
	The manual patching strategy is same with the DFix fastforward patch.
